<mjml>
  <mj-head>
    <mj-title>Thank You for Supporting {DATA_VARIABLE:projectName} - Receipt</mj-title>
    <mj-attributes>
      <mj-text font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="16px" line-height="1.6" color="#2D3534" />
      <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" />
    </mj-attributes>
  </mj-head>
  
  <mj-body background-color="#f4f4f4">
    
    <!-- Header with Logo -->
    <mj-section background-color="#2D3534" border-radius="8px 8px 0 0" padding="30px 20px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image 
          src="https://www.theinertiaproject.com/Inertia-Logo-Alternate-2-w-tagline.png" 
          alt="Inertia Logo" 
          width="250px" 
          href="https://theinertiaproject.com/"
        />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    
    <!-- Main Content -->
    <mj-section padding="40px 30px">
      <mj-column>
        
        <!-- Thank You Header -->
        <mj-text align="center" font-size="32px" font-weight="bold" color="#2D3534" padding-bottom="30px">
          Thank You for Your Support!
        </mj-text>
        
        <!-- Greeting -->
        <mj-text padding-bottom="20px">
          What up {DATA_VARIABLE:customerName}!
        </mj-text>
        
        <!-- Success Message -->
        <mj-text padding-bottom="20px">
          Your contribution to the <strong style="color: #64918E;">{DATA_VARIABLE:projectName}</strong> campaign has been successfully processed â€” and just like that, you're officially part of the The Inertia Project!
        </mj-text>
        
        <mj-text padding-bottom="20px">
          Thank you for supporting this campaign and for backing independent artists in a way that truly matters. Because of you, this music video is moving from idea to reality â€” and you now have a front-row seat as it comes to life.
        </mj-text>
        
        <mj-text font-weight="bold" padding-bottom="15px">
          Here's what's coming next:
        </mj-text>
        
        <mj-text padding-bottom="10px" line-height="1.4">
          <div style="padding-left: 30px;">
            ðŸŽŸ An invitation to {DATA_VARIABLE:artistName}'s exclusive supporter community at the conclusion of the fundraise<br/>
            ðŸŽ¥ Behind-the-scenes and VIP-only content from the video creation process<br/>
            ðŸ‘€ First-hand updates on the progress of the music video, from concept to final cut<br/>
            ðŸ”¥ Exclusive {DATA_VARIABLE:artistName} moments and insights fans won't see anywhere else
          </div>
        </mj-text>
        
        <mj-text padding-bottom="20px">
          This isn't just about watching the finished video â€” it's about being part of the journey, the build, and the life behind it.
        </mj-text>
        
        <mj-text padding-bottom="15px">
          Keep an eye on your inbox â€” your first insider update is coming soon.
        </mj-text>
        
        <!-- Thank You Note with Video -->
        <mj-text background-color="#fff8e1" border="1px solid #ffcc02" border-radius="6px" padding="20px 20px 10px 20px">
          <h3 style="margin: 0 0 15px 0; color: #64918E; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">
            A Personal Thank You from {DATA_VARIABLE:artistName}
          </h3>
        </mj-text>
        
        <mj-image
          src="{DATA_VARIABLE:videoThumbnailUrl}"
          alt="Thank you video from {DATA_VARIABLE:artistName}"
          href="{DATA_VARIABLE:videoUrl}"
          align="center"
          width="500px"
          padding="0px"
        />
        
        <mj-text background-color="#fff8e1" border="1px solid #ffcc02" border-top="0" border-radius="0 0 6px 6px" padding="10px 20px 20px 20px">
          <p style="margin: 0; text-align: center; color: #64918E; font-size: 12px; font-style: italic;">
            Click above to watch the video
          </p>
        </mj-text>
        
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Receipt Details Box -->
    <mj-section background-color="#f8f9fa" border="2px solid #CB945E" border-radius="8px" padding="25px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text font-size="18px" font-weight="bold" color="#2D3534" padding-bottom="15px">
          Receipt Details
        </mj-text>
        
        <mj-table>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
            <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong style="color: #2D3534;">Project:</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; text-align: right;"><span style="color: #64918E; font-weight: bold;">{DATA_VARIABLE:projectName}</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
            <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong style="color: #2D3534;">Artist:</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; text-align: right;">{DATA_VARIABLE:artistName}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
            <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong style="color: #2D3534;">Support Tier:</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; text-align: right;">{DATA_VARIABLE:tierName}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
            <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong style="color: #2D3534;">Amount:</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; text-align: right;"><span style="color: #22C55E; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px;">${DATA_VARIABLE:amount}</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
            <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong style="color: #2D3534;">Transaction ID:</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; text-align: right;"><span style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px;">{DATA_VARIABLE:transactionId}</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong style="color: #2D3534;">Date:</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; text-align: right;">{DATA_VARIABLE:paymentDate}</td>
          </tr>
        </mj-table>
        
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Why Crowdfunding Matters -->
    <mj-section padding="30px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text font-size="20px" font-weight="bold" color="#64918E" padding-bottom="15px">
          Why Music Crowdfunding Matters
        </mj-text>
        
        <mj-text padding-bottom="20px">
          By supporting {DATA_VARIABLE:artistName}, you're not just funding musicâ€”you're investing in artistic independence and authentic creativity. Your contribution helps artists stay true to their vision while building sustainable careers.
        </mj-text>
        
        <mj-text font-weight="bold" padding-bottom="5px">
          STAY INDIE!
        </mj-text>
        
        <mj-text>
          The Inertia Team
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    
    <!-- Footer -->
    <mj-section background-color="#2D3534" border-radius="0 0 8px 8px" padding="30px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text align="center" color="#ffffff" font-size="16px" font-weight="bold" padding-bottom="20px">
          Need help or have questions?
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text align="center" color="#ffffff" font-size="14px" padding-bottom="20px">
          Contact our support team at 
          <a href="mailto:team@theinertiaproject.com" style="color: #CB945E; text-decoration: none;">
            team@theinertiaproject.com
          </a>
        </mj-text>
        
        <mj-divider border-color="#64918E" border-width="1px" />
        
        <mj-text align="center" color="#ffffff" font-size="12px" line-height="1.5" padding-top="20px">
          Â© 2026 The Inertia Project. All rights reserved.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text align="center" color="#ffffff" font-size="12px" padding-top="10px">
          <a href="https://theinertiaproject.com/" target="_blank" style="color: #CB945E; text-decoration: none;">Visit Inertia</a> | 
          <a href="https://theinertiaproject.com/account" target="_blank" style="color: #CB945E; text-decoration: none;">My Account</a> | 
          <a href="mailto:team@theinertiaproject.com" style="color: #CB945E; text-decoration: none;">Contact Us</a>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    
  </mj-body>
</mjml>